ygData.messageBody:
Depends on if you wanna stick with soloing or
start grouping. I personally hate soloing. It is sooo
boring.<br><br>Grouping i would suggest the ever popular and crowded
Velk's Lab, Chardok, Sebilis, Karnor's Castle, Fungus
Grove, The Grey, Maiden's Eye, Scarlet Desert, or
Howling Stones.<br><br>Solo i would prob attempt Howling
Stones, although it may still be a bit tough. I solod the
entrance for awhile until i couldnt stand the boredom
anymore.<br><br>Few more solo spots: Burning Woods and the Grey. Cant
really think of anymore (been awhile since I was lvl
54).
